              "free_text": [
                " Average values of post",
                " neutron-emission energies for fragments from U-235",
                " thermal-neutron-induced fission.",
                "The kinetic energy spectrum of 235U thermalneutron-",
                "induced fission was measured, in order to check the",
                "saturation characteristics of pulse height and to",
                "calibrate the energies of fragments from",
                "238U spontaneous fission.",
                " (AM-BE) An Am-Be neutron source, thermalized by a",
                " paraffin wall of 30 cm thickness, used for satura-",
                " tion characteristics and energy calibration."
              ]
            }
